OL,3,CGap in orders at Hitachi factory
OL,4,Cprompt concerns over its future
OL,6,FThe Government say it is committed to
OL,7,Fsecuring the future of the Hitachi
OL,8,Ftrain factory in Newton Aycliffe amid
OL,9,Fconcerns over its future.
OL,11,FThe site faces a gap in orders with
OL,12,Fwork on existing contracts expected to
OL,13,Fdecline by October, leaving the
OL,14,FJapanese manufacturer "reviewing all
OL,15,Foptions" for the future.
OL,17,FAround 750 people are currently
OL,18,Femployed at the factory.
