OL,6,FThere have been calls for the
OL,7,FGovernment to sign off on new train
OL,8,Forders for the factory and the issue
OL,9,Fwas raised in Parliament by
OL,10,FConservative MP for Sedgefield Paul
OL,11,FHowell during Prime Minister's
OL,12,Fquestions on Wednesday (17 April).
OL,14,FIn response, Rishi Sunak said: "The
OL,15,FDepartment for Transport and the
OL,16,FSecretary of State have been actively
OL,17,Fengaged with companies to ensure we
OL,18,Fhave a robust supply chain.
