OL,3,CGap in orders at Hitachi factory
OL,4,Cprompt concerns over its future
OL,6,F"We're investing record amounts in
OL,7,Frail investment, particularly in the
OL,8,Fnorth, and we're pleased to see that's
OL,9,Fbeing delivered."
OL,11,FThe Department for Transport later
OL,12,Fconfirmed that it had held
OL,13,F"constructive" talks with union
OL,14,Frepresentatives for the Hitachi
OL,15,Fworkforce and "remain committed to
OL,16,Fsecure a sustainable future for rail
OL,17,Fmanufacturing at Newton Aycliffe".
