OL,3,CGap in orders at Hitachi factory
OL,4,Cprompt concerns over its future
OL,6,FHowever, the main workers union,
OL,7,FUnite, have called on the Government
OL,8,F"to pull its finger out" and award an
OL,9,Fextension of the contract to build
OL,10,Ftrains for the West Coast mainline to
OL,11,FHitachi immediately.
OL,13,FThe calls have been echoed by the
OL,14,FLabour MP for Easington Grahame Morris.
OL,16,F"I want them to accelerate the
OL,17,Forders," he told ITV Tyne Tees. "I
OL,18,Fwant them to have a truncated process
OL,19,Fto ensure that there is work in these
OL,20,Ffactories.
