OL,4,Cprompt concerns over its future
OL,6,F"Obviously Newton Aycliffe's next door
OL,7,Fto me, and some of my constituents
OL,8,Fwork either directly for Hitachi or in
OL,9,Fthe supply chain."
OL,11,FHitachi says it is committed to
OL,12,Ffinding a way forward for the County
OL,13,FDurham site despite the uncertainty.
OL,15,FA Hitachi Rail spokesperson said: "The
OL,16,FNorth East skills base and supply
OL,17,Fchain we have built has delivered
OL,18,Fsocial value and levelling-up.
OL,19,FMaintaining these benefits is in the
OL,20,Fnational interest.
