OL,6,F"Despite the lack of certainty, we
OL,7,Fremain committed to working with all
OL,8,Fstakeholders to find a viable way
OL,9,Fforward for our state-of-the-art
OL,10,Fmanufacturing facility in Newton
OL,11,FAycliffe.
OL,13,F"Preserving regional skills and supply
OL,14,Fchain will allow us to be competitive
OL,15,Fin future procurements and support
OL,16,FBritish economic growth."
